---

<BaseLayout title="Resume" sideBarActiveItemID="cv">
  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Profile</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10 text-left">
    <b>Growth Marketing and Product Specialist</b> with 8+ years driving digital
    transformation and business scaling. Founder of <a href="https://vehement.co">vehement.co</a> and <a href="https://hazlolatam.com">hazlolatam.com</a>,
    a thriving community for LATAM entrepreneurs. Expert in product development,
    B2B marketing automation, and growth engineering with a proven track record of
    taking startups from concept to market leadership. <br /><br />

    <b>Specialized in rapid prototyping through no-code/low-code platforms</b> and
    early AI adoption for enhanced productivity and innovation. Proficient across
    modern tools including Bubble, Webflow, Framer, Cursor, and Bolt, enabling accelerated
    development cycles and seamless product iterations. Advanced analytics capabilities
    with hands-on experience in conversion optimization, marketing attribution modeling,
    and translating complex datasets into actionable growth strategies. <br
    /><br />

    Passionate about leveraging cutting-edge AI tools to transform innovative
    ideas into scalable solutions while leading cross-functional teams to
    deliver exceptional results. Dedicated to mentoring entrepreneurs and teams,
    helping them harness the power of no-code technologies and artificial
    intelligence to achieve measurable ROI and exceed growth targets.
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
